"},"usefulItems":"baking tray and paper, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Saffron yoghurt is a good accompaniment to many Persian rice dishes. It will also work well alongside the lentils and rice with fried onions recipe in this collection."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","50m","4 portion"]}